T engineering students and companies.</p>"}}]},"projects":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Electric Vehicle Adoption Model","tech":["Vensim"],"github":"https://github.com/vascoalramos/ev-adoption-model","gitlab":null,"external":null},"html":"<p>A System Dynamics Model for the adoption process of Electric Vehicles from a consumer perspective.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Image Face Detection","tech":["Jupyter Notebook","Tensorflow","Keras","LaTeX"],"github":"https://github.com/vascoalramos/image-face-detection","gitlab":null,"external":null},"html":"<p>A comparison of Face Detection applications based on SVM and NN.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Air Quality","tech":["Spring Boot","Java","Thymeleaf","Bootstrap","WeatherBit API","BreezoMeter API","GitLab CI/CD"],"github":"https://github.com/vascoalramos/air-quality-service","gitlab":"https://gitlab.com/vascoalramos/air-quality-service","external":"https://tqs-air-quality-service.herokuapp.com/"},"html":"<p>A platform to check air quality metrics for specific cities. It also allows choosing the desired day of the data to be analyzed. Includes a caching system to speed up requests.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Authenticated File Transfer","tech":["Python","X.509 Certificates"],"github":"https://github.com/vascoalramos/authenticated-file-transfer","gitlab":null,"external":null},"html":"<p>An implementation of a client-server architecture with secure and authenticated communication used to send files from clients to the server.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Change Keeper","tech":["Java","Android"],"github":"https://github.com/vascoalramos/change-keeper","gitlab":null,"external":null},"html":"<p>An android mobile app to easily manage day-to-day money activities.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"My Game Stack","tech":["Microsoft SQL Server","C#"],"github":"https://github.com/vascoalramos/my-game-stack","gitlab":null,"external":null},"html":"<p>A games database with info about games, publishers, developers, platforms, reviews and others, with an interface to showcase the features and use cases of our system.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Dim X - Dimensional Analysis","tech":["Java","ANTLR4","Bash"],"github":"https://github.com/vascoalramos/dimX","gitlab":null,"external":null},"html":"<p>An implementation of a language capable to compute the task of dimensional analysis (an important issue of the physic's domain).</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Distributed Map Reduce","tech":["Python","Bash"],"github":"https://github.com/vascoalramos/distributed-map-reduce","gitlab":null,"external":null},"html":"<p>An implementation of the map/reduce algorithm in a centralized distributed system, with one coordinator and several workers processes, with a fault tolerance mechanism.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Bomberman AI Agent","tech":["Python"],"github":"https://github.com/vascoalramos/bomberman-ai","gitlab":null,"external":null},"html":"<p>An implementation of an AI agent, using A* Search Algorithm, to win the bomberman game.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"P2P Drive-Through","tech":["Python","Bash"],"github":"https://github.com/vascoalramos/dimX","gitlab":null,"external":null},"html":"<p>An implementation of a drive-through restaurant using a peer-to-peer distributed system architecture.</p>"}}]},"hero":{"frontmatter":{"salute":"Hi, my name is","name":"Vasco Ramos,","micro_bio":"I'm a Computer Science Student.","cta":"About Me"}},"about":{"html":"<p>Hello! I'm Vasco Ramos, a 21-year-old student at the University of Minho, from the district of Viseu. I already graduated from my 3-year Bachelor's Degree in the fields of Computer Science and Software Engineering at the University of Aveiro, and I am currently taking my Mater's Degree in the same fields at the University of Minho.</p>\n<p>I'm passionate about Databases, Software Engineering, Web and Micro Services, DevOps and Data Engineering.</p>\n<p>During these years at the University of Aveiro, I always tried to enrich my academic path with other activities such as volunteer work and associativism within the university. With that in mind, I am a mentor to first-year students.</p>\n<p>Furthermore, since my second year, I am part of an organization called <a href=\"http://aettua.pt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" title=\"AETTUA\">AETTUA</a>, a non-profit youth association that aims to promote the most diverse activities for all students, teachers and employees of our department (<a href=\"https://www.ua.pt/deti\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" title=\"DETI\">DETI</a>).</p>\n<p>With this experience, I had the chance to organize workshops, trips to a bunch of company's headquarters and job fairs. I consider this work one of the most important things I did during college because it allowed me to improve my social skills, such as teamwork and people management.</p>\n<p>Driven by the desire of always being my better self, I choose to be in constant learning and having an open mind.</p>\n<p>Lastly, I consider myself a goal-oriented person, always focused on a problem and my mantra of life is all about hard work and absolute determination.</p>","frontmatter":{"image":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","width":300,"height":300,"src":"/static/63ac2d016169083da770a239ef9d915e/9dc27/profile.jpg","srcSet":"/static/63ac2d016169083da770a239ef9d915e/9dc27/profile.jpg 1x,\n/static/63ac2d016169083da770a239ef9d915e/32fd5/profile.jpg 1.5x,\n/static/63ac2d016169083da770a239ef9d915e/4fe8c/profile.jpg 2x"}}},"resume":"resume.pdf"}}}}